                    <title>I like to bring up the Wikipe…</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://coderetreat.org/xn/detail/6456126:Comment:2164"/>
                                        <id>tag:coderetreat.org,2011-11-28:6456126:Comment:2164</id>
                                        <updated>2011-11-28T17:38:08.992Z</updated>
                    
                                            <author>
                            <name>Jim Hurne</name>
                            <uri>http://coderetreat.org/profile/JimHurne</uri>
                        </author>
                    
                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;I like to bring up the Wikipedia page for the Game of Life and project it on the wall during the sessions. I also encourage pairs to pull up the Wikipedia page on one of their laptops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If nether of those options will work, you could print the rules out and hand them out to each pair.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jim++&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;I like to bring up the Wikipedia page for the Game of Life and project it on the wall during the sessions. I also encourage pairs to pull up the Wikipedia page on one of their laptops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If nether of those options will work, you could print the rules out and hand them out to each pair.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jim++&lt;/p&gt;                        </content>
                    
